# DRAFT Workspace — CODEOWNERS
#
# Generated by DRAFT setup-mode. Replace getdraft with your GitHub organization
# slug and update team handles to match your GitHub Teams before enabling
# branch protection on main.
#
# Three DRAFT roles map to three ownership tiers:
#
#   draft-admins     — workspace config, vocabulary, requirement groups
#   shared-services  — shared technology catalog (tech components, runtime
#                      services, hosts, data store services, network services)
#   engineering      — product components, data components, SDPs
#
# ── Draft Admins ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Owns the framework vendoring, workspace config, and vocabulary governance.

.draft/                                  @getdraft/draft-admins
.github/                                 @getdraft/draft-admins
configurations/                          @getdraft/draft-admins
catalog/governance/                      @getdraft/draft-admins

# ── Shared Services ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Owns the shared technology catalog. Engineering teams reference these objects
# in their SDPs; they do not modify them directly.

catalog/shared-services/technology-components/  @getdraft/shared-services
catalog/shared-services/runtime-services/        @getdraft/shared-services
catalog/shared-services/hosts/                   @getdraft/shared-services
catalog/shared-services/data-store-services/     @getdraft/shared-services
catalog/shared-services/network-services/        @getdraft/shared-services
catalog/governance/decision-records/             @getdraft/shared-services @getdraft/draft-admins

# ── Engineering ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Each engineering team owns their product components, data components, and
# SDPs. Add one line per team. If using a team-first folder structure
# (catalog/engineering/[team]/), one line covers all three object types.
#
# Team-first structure (recommended):
#   catalog/engineering/[team-slug]/     @getdraft/[github-team-slug]
#
# Object-type structure (default seeded layout):
#   catalog/engineering/product-components/           @getdraft/engineering-team
#   catalog/engineering/data-components/              @getdraft/engineering-team
#   catalog/engineering/software-deployment-patterns/ @getdraft/engineering-team
#
# Example team-first lines — replace with your teams:
# catalog/engineering/absence-management/  @getdraft/absence-management
# catalog/engineering/benefits-delivery/   @getdraft/benefits-delivery
# catalog/engineering/platform/            @getdraft/platform-engineering
